data.title: Who are some famous people from Hull, England?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 8): The name of this city is Kingston upon Hull, shortened to Hull. Here is a link to famous people from there: List of people from Kingston upon Hull - Wikipedia

My favourite is my poet hero, Philip Larkin, who wrote one of the best, searingly accurate modern poems:

They fuck you ...
